Titolo: Phantom of the Asteroid

Anno: 1986

Descrizione: Phantom of the Asteroid is a side-scrolling action-adventure game released for the Commodore 64 in 1986. The cover art reads Phantom of the Asteroids, but the loading screen says Phantom of the Asteroid, while the title screen says Phantoms of the Asteroid. Sources variously use all three titles to refer to the game.